1 SECTION 2. A new section to chapter 50-24.1 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
2 and enacted as follows:
3 Medical assistance benefits - Postpartum doula services.
4 1. Medical assistance coverage, including Medicaid expansion coverage, must include
5 coverage of postpartum doula services, as defined in section 1 of this Act.
6 2. The department shall provide notice to an enrollee regarding the coverage required by
7 this section.
